4. Immediately return to an upright position. Repeat for the desired number of repetitions.', 'https://www.bodybuilding.com/exercises/exerciseImages/sequences/769/Male/l/769_1.jpg, https://www.bodybuilding.com/exercises/exerciseImages/sequences/769/Male/l/769_2.jpg, https://www.bodybuilding.com/exercises/exerciseImages/sequences/769/Male/l/769_3.jpg', 'https://artifacts.bbcomcdn.com/@bbcom/exercises-app/2.1.2/img/guide-1.gif');
    
